1938;;Save a Little Sunshine;;British;;Norman Lee;;Patricia Kirkwood, Tommy Trinder;;comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Save_a_Little_Sunshine;;After he is sacked from his job, Dave Smalley buys a share in a hotel, but has to resort to working there when all other financial schemes fail. His girlfriend Pat however, comes up with the idea of turning the property into a smart restaurant, and business takes off beyond all expectation.